<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="as-it-is-was">as it is / was</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[置于句首] 实际上；[置于句末] 已经：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As it is, I have a garden full of sweet-smelling roses for most of the year.
其实，我有一座花园，一年中大部分时间都玫瑰飘香。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ve already gone into debt as it is, so don’t expect any more money from me.
我已经欠债了，所以不要指望我会再出钱。</p></div></div>